text: Koxinga - Lord with the Imperial Surname is the traditional Western spelling of Zheng Chenggong (1624 - 1662). Koxinga was a leader at the end of the Chinese Ming Dynasty. He defeated the Dutch to claim Taiwan in 1662 at the Siege of Fort Zeelandia. ==Related pages== * Siege of Fort Zeelandia ==References== Category:History of Taiwan Category:1624 births Category:1662 deaths Category:History of China Category:Chinese military people Category:17th-century Chinese people
